# Grafana Dashboards Index

Welcome to the Grafana Dashboard Index. Below, you'll find an organized view of all available dashboards categorized for easy navigation.

## Dashboard Categories

| Category                           | Dashboard Description                               | Link                                          |
|------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------|
| **Server-Specific Metrics**        |                                                    |                                               |
| Server Memory Usage                | Memory usage metrics for the server                | [View Dashboard](/d/cdd71a29-8e29-4608-ac80-4f94741f63e4/container_memory_usage_bytes{name="server"}) |
| Server Cumulative CPU Time         | Cumulative CPU time consumed by the server         | [View Dashboard](/d/fbad3f40-4404-43b4-a8de-a03a08cd4ef9/container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{name="server"}) |
| Model Accuracy                     | Model accuracy as reported by the server           | [View Dashboard](/d/f63a7d0f-d29a-4a2e-b748-7bb66f9c17d7/model_accuracy{instance="server:8000"}) |
| Model Loss                         | Model loss as reported by the server               | [View Dashboard](/d/b697e6b8-0590-4ffb-a4f3-d14f004fb6ce/model_loss{instance="server:8000"}) |
| **Client-Specific Metrics**        |                                                    |                                               |
| Memory Usage                       | Insights into `client1` memory usage               | [View Dashboard](/d/cd0d5026-20aa-4614-9dfe-0c14f1d6522f/container_memory_usage_bytes{name="client1"})  |
| Cumulative CPU Time                | Cumulative CPU time consumed by `client1`          | [View Dashboard](/d/be38333d-f7bb-40c9-809f-662d1e27fbad/container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{name="client1"}) |
| Cumulative Packets Received                | Cumulative count of packets received by `client1`          | [View Dashboard](/d/a6be6c63-6243-4d55-99d9-1db2d9f5f6d5/container_network_receive_packets_total{name="client1"}) |
| Cumulative Packets transmitted                | Cumulative count of packets transmitted by `client1`          | [View Dashboard](/d/c30ee11e-5cfc-4d93-a76b-410c2cb05909/container_network_transmit_packets_total{name="client1"})|
